---
<section id="proyectos" class="py-24 scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-dali-dark uppercase tracking-tight">Proyectos Seleccionados</h2>
    <p class="text-dali-dark/60 font-medium mt-3">Una muestra de ideas transformadas en experiencias web fluidas y estéticas.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="group cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-dali-rose/10 border border-dali-dark/5 aspect-video rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(61,52,46,0.02)] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2 group-hover:shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(61,52,46,0.08)] flex items-center justify-center text-6xl select-none">
        🌿
      </div>
      <div class="mt-5 px-2">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-dali-toast">Diseño & Frontend</span>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-dali-dark mt-1">Studio Flora</h3>
        <p class="text-dali-dark/70 font-medium text-sm mt-1">E-commerce minimalista y cozy para un vivero boutique local.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="group cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-dali-matcha/10 border border-dali-dark/5 aspect-video rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(61,52,46,0.02)] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2 group-hover:shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(61,52,46,0.08)] flex items-center justify-center text-6xl select-none">
        ☕
      </div>
      <div class="mt-5 px-2">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-dali-toast">Desarrollo Astro</span>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-dali-dark mt-1">Café Circular</h3>
        <p class="text-dali-dark/70 font-medium text-sm mt-1">Landing page ultra veloz con animaciones sutiles para una tostaduría.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>